    {
        "id": 271182941,
        "number": 5,
        "title": "Confusing in  self._callbacks of Fulture",
        "state": "closed",
        "created_at": "2017-11-04T10:45:07Z",
        "updated_at": "2017-11-07T09:48:39Z",
        "closed_at": "2017-11-07T09:48:39Z",
        "author": "Gypsying",
        "comments": 2,
        "labels": [],
        "assignees": [],
        "locked": false,
        "body": "前辈您好，\r\nFulture类中您用了列表类型来保存  Task.step() 函数，\r\n但是每个Fulture 只有一个回调函数啊，为什么要用列表呢？\r\n我试着改了下：\r\n\r\n```\r\nclass Future:\r\n    def __init__(self):\r\n        self.result = None\r\n        self._callback = None\r\n\r\n    def add_done_callback(self, fn):\r\n        self._callback = fn\r\n\r\n    def set_result(self, result):\r\n        self.result = result\r\n        if self._callback:\r\n            self._callback(self)\r\n```\r\n\r\n感觉这样更简单啊，在下小白一个，请帮忙解惑 ^_^\r\n",
        "url": "https://github.com/denglj/aiotutorial/issues/5"
    }
]